These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
City: marseilles, boston, liverpool
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| City   | boston | liverpool | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Flower   | tulip | lily | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
